author: Top Gear
description:
In 2024, The Stig set a stunning lap time at the Top Gear Test Track in unhinged Ford’s SuperVan 4.2, catapulting it into fourth place overall, behind only open-wheeled Formula cars and the mad McMurtry Spéirling. Now though, Ford has a new ‘electric vehicle demonstrator’, the F-150 Lightning SuperTruck, which boasts over 2000bhp, along with more downforce and less weight than its predecessor. This should be brisk…

🚗 Ford F-150 Lightning SuperTruck
